snippet.title: New Super Mario Bros. U Deluxe - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Join Mario, Luigi, and some new pals like Nabbit and Toadette for single-player or multiplayer fun anytime, anywhere! Available January 11, 2019.

Learn more about New Super Mario Bros. U Deluxe! https://goo.gl/4TwDf4
